<i>adverb</i>: 흠씬 [흠씬], 혹독히 [혹또키], 푹 [푹], 통절히 [통ː절히], 지독히 [지도키], 지독스레 [지독쓰레], 중히 [중ː히], 엄히 [엄히], 엄중히 [엄중히], 심히 [심ː히], 심각히 [심ː가키], 마구마구 [마구마구], 마구 [마구], 딥다 [딥따], 들입다 [드립따], 단단히 [단단히], 내리 [내리], 극렬히 [긍녈히 ] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흠씬 [흠씬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. sufficiently; fully; greatly</dd><br>
<dd>꽉 차고도 남을 만큼 넉넉하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being ample to the extent of overflowing.</dd><br>
<dd>2. to the skin; completely; thoroughly</dd><br>
<dd>물에 푹 젖은 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of being soaked.</dd><br>
<dd>3. severely; harshly; excessively</dd><br>
<dd>매우 심하게 때리거나 맞는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of beating someone or being beaten severely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>혹독히 [혹또키]</dt><br>
<dd>1. harshly; severely; bitterly</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of being excessively severe.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cruelly; mercilessly; harshly</dd><br>
<dd>성질이나 하는 짓이 몹시 모질고 악하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of one's personality or actions being extremely wicked and heartless.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푹 [푹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. soundly</dd><br>
<dd>잠이 깊이 들거나 피곤한 몸을 충분히 편하게 쉬는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing an act of falling asleep or taking a good rest to recover from fatigue.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with a thrust</dd><br>
<dd>힘 있게 깊이 찌르거나 쑤시는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing an act of stabbing or poking something strongly and deeply.</dd><br>
<dd>3. well; completely</dd><br>
<dd>안의 것이 드러나지 않도록 빈틈없이 아주 잘 덮거나 싸는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing an act of covering or wrapping something without any missing part, so that the content cannot be seen.</dd><br>
<dd>4. enough; well</dd><br>
<dd>충분히 익도록 삶거나 고거나 끓이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing an act of steaming, simmering, or boiling something until it is completely cooked.</dd><br>
<dd>5. completely; severely</dd><br>
<dd>아주 심하게 썩거나 삭거나 젖은 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of something being seriously rotten, fermented, or wet.</dd><br>
<dd>6. deeply</dd><br>
<dd>깊고 뚜렷하게 파인 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of something being deeply and clearly dug or sunken.</dd><br>
<dd>7. deeply; completely</dd><br>
<dd>아주 깊이 빠지거나 잠기는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of something deeply falling or sinking into a place.</dd><br>
<dd>8. heavily</dd><br>
<dd>힘없이 단번에 쓰러지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing an act of falling heavily and instantly.</dd><br>
<dd>9. fully</dd><br>
<dd>삽이나 숟가락 등으로 물건을 아주 많이 떠내는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing an act of scooping out a great quantity of things with a shovel, spoon, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>10. deeply</dd><br>
<dd>고개를 아주 깊이 숙이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing an act of bending one's head very deeply.</dd><br>
<dd>11. densely; much</dd><br>
<dd>연기나 가루 등이 세게 쏟아져 나오는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word imitating the sound made when powder, smoke, etc., strongly comes out through a hole, or describing such a scene.</dd><br>
<dd>12. suddenly; steeply</dd><br>
<dd>힘이나 능력 또는 분량 등이 갑자기 많이 줄어든 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of a power, ability, or quantity being greatly reduced.</dd><br>
<dd>13. completely</dd><br>
<dd>가루나 먼지 등이 꽤 많이 덮인 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of something being covered with much powder, dust, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>통절히 [통ː절히]</dt><br>
<dd>keenly; severely; acutely</dd><br>
<dd>고통이나 슬픔 등이 뼛속에 파고들 정도로 매우 깊고 강하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In deep pain or sorrow, etc., which hurts to the bone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>지독히 [지도키]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spitefully; venomously</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 성격이 매우 모질고 독하며 매섭게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's mind or personality being very cold and harsh.</dd><br>
<dd>2. potently; strongly</dd><br>
<dd>맛이나 냄새 등이 해롭거나 참기 어려울 정도로 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of the taste, smell, etc., being intolerably harmful or strong.</dd><br>
<dd>3. extremely; incredibly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨나 기온 등이 일정한 정도를 넘은 정도로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of weather, climate, etc., being beyond a certain degree.</dd><br>
<dd>4. extremely; incredibly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 모양이나 상태 등이 극에 달한 정도로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of an appearance or situation being very extreme.</dd><br>
<dd>5. severely</dd><br>
<dd>병이 더할 수 없을 정도로 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of illness or soreness being severe beyond words.</dd><br>
<dd>6. firmly</dd><br>
<dd>의지나 마음이 매우 크고 강하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of a person's having a strong will.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>지독스레 [지독쓰레]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spitefully; venomously</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 성격이 매우 모질고 독하며 매서운 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's mind or personality being very cold and harsh.</dd><br>
<dd>2. potently; strongly</dd><br>
<dd>맛이나 냄새 등이 해롭거나 참기 어려울 정도로 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of the taste, smell, etc., being intolerably harmful or strong.</dd><br>
<dd>3. extremely; incredibly</dd><br>
<dd>날씨나 기온 등이 일정한 정도를 넘은 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of weather, climate, etc., being beyond a certain degree.</dd><br>
<dd>4. extremely; incredibly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 모양이나 상태 등이 극에 달한 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of an appearance or situation being very extreme.</dd><br>
<dd>5. severely</dd><br>
<dd>병이 더할 수 없을 정도로 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of illness or soreness being severe beyond words.</dd><br>
<dd>6. firmly</dd><br>
<dd>의지나 마음이 매우 크고 강한 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of a person's having a strong will.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>중히 [중ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. preciously</dd><br>
<dd>매우 중요하고 소중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With respect and care.</dd><br>
<dd>2. severely</dd><br>
<dd>대단하거나 크게. 또는 무겁게.</dd><br>
<dd>Greatly, seriously or gravely.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄히 [엄히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. severely; rigorously</dd><br>
<dd>규칙을 적용하거나 예절을 가르치는 일 등이 매우 철저하고 바르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very thorough and right manner in applying a rule or teaching etiquette.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rigorously; strictly</dd><br>
<dd>일이나 행동이 잘못되지 않도록 주의가 철저하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a thoroughly careful manner so that something does not go wrong or one does not behave wrongly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>엄중히 [엄중히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. strictly; stringently; sternly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 엄하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very strict manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. strictly</dd><br>
<dd>엄격하고 정중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Sternly and politely.</dd><br>
<dd>3. severely</dd><br>
<dd>그냥 넘길 수 없을 정도로 중대하게.</dd><br>
<dd>So seriously as to be hard to overlook.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>심히 [심ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>severely; harshly</dd><br>
<dd>정도가 지나치게.</dd><br>
<dd>To an excessive degree.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>심각히 [심ː가키]</dt><br>
<dd>seriously; severely</dd><br>
<dd>상태나 정도가 매우 심하거나 절박하거나 중대하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which a state or degree is very severe, urgent, or important.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>마구마구 [마구마구]</dt><br>
<dd>1. severely</dd><br>
<dd>계속해서 매우 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very seriously, continuously.</dd><br>
<dd>2. randomly</dd><br>
<dd>계속해서 아무렇게나 되는대로.</dd><br>
<dd>At random continuously without a rule or plan.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>마구 [마구]</dt><br>
<dd>1. severely</dd><br>
<dd>매우 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very seriously.</dd><br>
<dd>2. randomly</dd><br>
<dd>아무렇게나 되는대로.</dd><br>
<dd>At random without a rule or plan.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>딥다 [딥따]</dt><br>
<dd>extremely; severely</dd><br>
<dd>심하게 마구.</dd><br>
<dd>In an excessive and wild manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>들입다 [드립따]</dt><br>
<dd>extremely; severely</dd><br>
<dd>심하게 마구.</dd><br>
<dd>In an excessive and wild manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>단단히 [단단히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hard</dd><br>
<dd>사물이 어떤 힘에 의해 모양이 변하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>(an object) Hard enough not to be changed by a certain force.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hard; solidly</dd><br>
<dd>약하거나 무르지 않고 빈틈이 없이 튼튼하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Evenly solid, not weakly or softly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. firmly</dd><br>
<dd>속이 꽉 차서 야무지고 실속이 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>Fully, firmly, and practically.</dd><br>
<dd>4. tightly; firmly</dd><br>
<dd>느슨하지 않고 튼튼하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Strongly, not loosely.</dd><br>
<dd>5. surely; strongly</dd><br>
<dd>뜻이나 생각이 흔들림 없이 강하게.</dd><br>
<dd>(one's will or thought maintained) Strongly, without being shaken.</dd><br>
<dd>6. seriously; severely</dd><br>
<dd>보통보다 더 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>More severely than normal.</dd><br>
<dd>7. surely</dd><br>
<dd>확실하게 제대로.</dd><br>
<dd>Done surely.</dd><br>
<dd>8. strongly</dd><br>
<dd>일의 기본 바탕이 튼튼하게.</dd><br>
<dd>(the ground for something made) Strongly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>내리 [내리]</dt><br>
<dd>1. successively; at a stretch; in a row</dd><br>
<dd>잇달아 계속해서.</dd><br>
<dd>Continuously one after another.</dd><br>
<dd>2. severely; wildly</dd><br>
<dd>사정없이 마구.</dd><br>
<dd>Violently without mercy.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>극렬히 [긍녈히 ]</dt><br>
<dd>keenly; severely</dd><br>
<dd>매우 심하게 사납고 세차게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a very severe, ferocious, and fierce manner.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>